      "content": "i feel like i'm just a hollow shell now. there's nothing left to give. i look at my life and it's just... empty. i just want to sleep. i just want to go to sleep and not have to worry about anything ever again. like, maybe if i just didn't wake up, this weight would finally be gone.",
